<ab facs="#facs_211_r2l6"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . beſant / vnd Jn <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brıef laſſen hören / vnd <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> hat vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r2l9"><expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / . wie die ſache <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jn beden 
