<del rend="strikethrough">den <expan>hochwirdıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>fürſt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den Byſchof <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan></del> des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r2l11">Künigreichs <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Beheim Kamrer / 
