<del rend="strikethrough">daʒ </del> was <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Arnolt doſelbſt <expan>gelaſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> hab / daʒ das Jn beden </ab>
