<del rend="strikethrough">gët </del> gütlıch vnd <expan>gencʒl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>miteinand<ex>er</ex></expan> gerıchtet ſein ſüllen / Als vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r2l18">der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> . einen <expan>geſıgelt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> brıef geweiſet hat des wir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r2l19">ew ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>ſend<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>beſloʒʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> an <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> brıef / . dabey <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
